'''富金'''（{{lang-de|Fugging}}，{{IPA-de|ˈfʊɡɪŋ}}）為奧地利的村落，位處[[下奧地利州|下奧地利州]][[圣珀尔滕兰县|圣珀尔滕兰县]][[奥布里茨贝格-鲁斯特|奥布里茨贝格-鲁斯特]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eventzz.net/Austria/Obritzberg-Rust/Fugging-Nieder%C3%B6sterreich-Austria |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111112204/http://eventzz.net/Austria/Obritzberg-Rust/Fugging-Nieder%C3%B6sterreich-Austria |archive-date=2014-01-11 |title=Fugging, Niederösterreich, Austria in Obritzberg-Rust - Lower Austria - Austria |publisher=Eventzz.net (archived) |accessdate=2014-01-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，改名前稱「Fucking」。

== 村名來歷==
富金的前稱「Fucking」首次於當地修道院教區在1195年的文獻記錄中所記載。1836年，因不明原因改名為「Fugging」<ref name=mirror>{{cite news |url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/fucking-village-told-cant-renamed-798433 |title=Fucking village told they can't be renamed Fugging because name is already taken |newspaper=[[每日镜报|每日镜报]] |date=2012-04-18 |accessdate=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308111004/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/fucking-village-told-cant-renamed-798433 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=at>{{cite web |url=http://austriantimes.at/news/General_News/2012-04-18/41033/No_Fugging_chance_for_name_change |title=No Fugging chance for name change |publisher=Austrian Times |date=2012-04-18 |accessdate=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111112133/http://austriantimes.at/news/General_News/2012-04-18/41033/No_Fugging_chance_for_name_change |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管改名原因不明，惟據當地村長推測，由於該地相較[[富金_(上奧地利州)|其他以Fucking為名的地區]]更接近維也納，因此操英語的遊客更有可能到此參訪，然而「Fucking」在英語中意指[[性交|性交]]，為[[Fuck|一種粗俗語]]。<ref name=mirror />當地的地名牌已牢固安裝，以防[[標誌盜竊|遭竊]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://noe.orf.at/news/stories/2529415/ |title=Fugging war auch einmal Fucking |publisher=noe.ORF.at |language=de |date=2012-04-17 |accessdate=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2017-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925132719/http://noe.orf.at/news/stories/2529415/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 設施 ==
富金境內設有一座教堂，1894年創設，1896年獻堂。該教堂的屋頂經歷多次的冰雹襲擊而受損，因此在1984年進行翻修<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.obritzberg-rust.gv.at/system/web/gelbeseite.aspx?typ=11&bezirkonr=0&detailonr=186154388&menuonr=220527770 |title=RiS-Kommunal - Dorfkapelle Fugging |publisher=Obritzberg-Rust |date= |accessdate=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924054420/http://www.obritzberg-rust.gv.at/system/web/gelbeseite.aspx?typ=11&bezirkonr=0&detailonr=186154388&menuonr=220527770 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，富金境內亦設有[[志愿消防局|志愿消防局]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.meinbezirk.at/sankt-poelten/leute/brennpunkt-fugging-im-geschehen-die-feuerwehr-d546033.html |title=Brennpunkt Fugging, im Geschehen die Feuerwehr - Sankt Pölten |language=de |publisher=meinbezirk.at |date= |accessdate=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111115435/http://www.meinbezirk.at/sankt-poelten/leute/brennpunkt-fugging-im-geschehen-die-feuerwehr-d546033.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

